data.description: ASSUMABLE 2.99% FHA Loan. This could save you $400 per month or more! Ask for more details.  You will appreciate this meticulously maintained 5-year-old home, boasting 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and 4,002 square feet of elegant living space. Nestled on a very private cul-de-sac, enjoy both privacy and ample parking. A welcoming foyer leads to a light-filled living room, perfect for a home office, and an open dining room for entertaining. The open and spacious design features a family room connecting seamlessly to the kitchen with granite countertops, stainless appliances, and a walk-in pantry. The luxurious owner's suite on the first floor includes a garden tub, separate shower, double sink vanity, and his and her walk-in closets. Additional conveniences on the first floor include a powder room and a walk-in laundry room. Upstairs, discover four bedrooms, a bonus room, and a loft area with two bathrooms, ensuring everyone has their own space. The fenced backyard with a storage shed and a 3-car attached tandem garage completes the outdoor paradise. Upgrades include engineered hardwood floors, ceramic tiles in the laundry and ensuite, and sophisticated 5.5-inch baseboards downstairs. Energy efficiency is prioritized with a 20-inch-thick attic insulation layer, ensuring comfort and cost-effective living.  This home conveniently provides easy access to Upstate's best offerings, including restaurants, events, markets, parks, and more. Don't miss this incredible opportunity! Schedule a private showing and experience the best of modern living in this beautiful community.
